title: S1 Ep17: Evidence to practice: Reforming private healthcare in India
itunes:title: Evidence to practice: Reforming private healthcare in India
description:
Using the example of healthcare in India, Nick O’Donohoe, Chief Executive Officer, CDC, discusses how data plays a crucial role in making sure investments are put to their best use.

Find out more at [VoxDev.org](https://voxdev.org/topic/health-education/evidence-practice-reforming-private-healthcare-india)
